citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 0930 Hours on
06-Dec-17.
I honked the horn and discovered that a German Shepherd was running loose and his mannerism let me know he
might bite, so I called and left a voicemail and then texted waited for a response.
